special_notes: Does not use the letter 'O' on standard tags. Letter 'O' and number '0' used on personalized tags. Letter 'O' is much rounder, number '0' is slimmer. Example tags: NY-LILY05 (fifth character is '0'), NY-EENSKOOT (sixth and seventh are 'O'), NY-527EMTP (EMTP keyed), NY-MD95409 (MD keyed), NY-VAS1128 (VAS keyed), NY-DAV999 (DAV keyed). State indicator (map) in center of tag.
